These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, cola
1. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Beverage   | cola | mirinda |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, social-worker
1. the librarian is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
2. the social-worker is on the right of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Job   | librarian | social-worker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: cooking, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | cooking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, electronic
1. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | r&b |

